/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com/thread/1714163/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<code>想知乜嘢叫流水式...集會?流水就不可能集合，集合可能是在新屋嶺... - #1</code><br />\n<blockquote>想知乜嘢叫流水式...集會?<br />\n流水就不可能集合，集合可能是在新屋嶺...<br />\n會唔會太過 creative, creative 到亂Q咁嚟。<br />\n定你哋較為喜愛嗌D無意思的口號，做無意義的事，好似時代革命，摺紙咁。</blockquote><a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1696584/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com/thread/1696584/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<code>改口號啦！[香港人！送頭！] - #1</code><br />\n<blockquote>香港人！送頭！<img src=\"http://www.lihkg.com/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lihkg.com%2Fassets%2Ffaces%2Fdog%2Fzzz.gif&h=b6af20bd&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1696549/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com/thread/1696549/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<code>點呀？之前係咪話過要追究返邊d人，邊d網，邊d團體同傳媒吹市去送頭既？ - #1</code><br />\n<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/T2b0VZQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FT2b0VZQ.jpg&h=2ac5df0e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n原來係連登x蘋果吹雞<br />\n難怪有哂地點時間表<br />\n鑊鑊都港島，鑊鑊都推人去死<br />\n流人哋嘅血成就自己得票當選！<br />\n泛民蘋果全部都要仆街冚家鏟！<br />\n<br />\n好彩我一早就同班泛民左膠割晒蓆姐，分化實在好！<img src=\"http://www.lihkg.com/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lihkg.com%2Fassets%2Ffaces%2Fnormal%2Fsmile.gif&h=0b593ebc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n快d回&quot;拉，不分化，不推文回覆啦&quot;<img src=\"http://www.lihkg.com/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lihkg.com%2Fassets%2Ffaces%2Fdog%2Fzzz.gif&h=b6af20bd&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1691882/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com/thread/1691882/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;pos